42:22.640 --> 42:27.077
There, there.
Sherman and George were good boys.

42:27.144 --> 42:29.078
We should be proud.

42:29.146 --> 42:33.913
And you got to know, Edmund,
you can't keep a Peacock down.

42:33.984 --> 42:36.077
There'll be more.

42:36.153 --> 42:39.418
One day, there'll be more.

42:39.490 --> 42:41.924
Now we have to move on,

42:41.992 --> 42:44.085
start a new family.

42:44.161 --> 42:46.254
One we'll be proud of.

42:46.330 --> 42:49.265
Find a new place to call ours.

42:49.333 --> 42:51.233
A new home.

